metadata.name: Omakase #1
metadata.description:
EDITION 1 OF 1

Title: Omakase  
Artist: Godwits  
Year: 2022

Omakase which translates in Japanese to "I leave it up to you." Godwits created a visual dining experience as a digital chef in the metaverse. Godwits has prepared a 100 piece sushi omakase meal with each piece being a unique 1/1 food art. Experimenting with 3D, AI & Graphic Design, We had a wonderful time creating this. Hope you're hungry and ready to eat sushi with your imagination. Enjoy!

Published By: Abstract Art Labs LLC  
Smart Contract By / Token Type: Manifold / ERC-721
